Tool used for Scanning infrastructure as code templates

Checkov  :  To detect cloud misconfigurations, it scans your cloud infrastructure, which is managed in Kubernetes, Terraform, and Cloudformation.

Example vulnerability:
EC2SecurityGroupMissingEgressRule : Missing egress rule in NoIngressSecurityGroup means all traffic is allowed outbound. Make this explicit if it is desired configuration


